<sect2> <title>MySQLAccess Reference</title>
 <sect3> <title>MySQLAccess environment variables</title>
  <itemizedlist>
   <listitem>
    <para>
    <emphasis role="bold">CORAL_MYSQL_CLOB_PREFIX_LEN</emphasis> :
    if set to a numeric value in the range from 0 to 255, it affects
    the orefix size of the index prefix of all the index column of the
    CLOB MySQL types like TINYTEXT, TEXT, MEDIUMTEXT &amp; LONGTEXT.
    If not set the default built-in prefix size is 32 bytes/chars.
    </para>
   </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
 </sect3>

